ABUSING HER).\] }]
[\In it, a man goes to a high loft to write a letter; women drink    #
with men at an inn.\] 

[$ (\Examinacio testium super libello ex parte Katerine Claiton,     #
partis
actricis, contra et aduersus Margaretam Tailiour, partem ream, capta
coram magistro Roberto Leche, &c, xj=o= die Aprilis, 1562.\) $]

   [$ (\Laurencius Manwaringe, parochie Vici-Malbani, etatis xxxv=t= 
