annorum, novit partem actricem a matrimonio inter Willelmum Claitton #
et
ipsam, et partem ream a natiuitate\) / $]
   [$ (\Ad primum articulum, credit eundem fore verum.\) $]
   [$ (\Ad ij=d= articulum, nescit deponere nisi ex auditu. Reddendo #
racionem
sui dicti\) , this deponent sais, that apon a Saterday in Septembre  # 
last,
at an after-none, this deponent beinge required bie one Browne, newly
